Tracks are downloaded off of a P2P.  This is not an official CD rip.

Decent upload.


For the computer illiterate -- 4 simple steps:

1.- Search and download Daemon Tools via google.

2.- Install Daemons and set up virtual CD rom drive.

3.- Mount Cascada ISO

4.- Open your virtual drive, then copy and paste folder to your desktop, and there you have it.
